&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity is available for those wanting to gain Band 5 experience in a fast paced and dynamic environment offering excellent support and development opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work as part of the in patient service based at the Royal Hampshire County Hospital Winchester promoting independence with the focus on providing safe and timely discharges from hospital. You will have the opportunity to develop your skills within Elderly Care, Medicine, Rapid Discharge, Orthopaedics and Stroke with support from Senior Occupational Therapists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Team are committed to supporting individuals with continued professional development offering: preceptorship, regular clinical and managerial supervision, and team development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We provide a service across 7 days so a commitment to 7 day working is essential. If you are interested in this role we would encourage you to come and meet the team and spend time with us in the working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
